FBIS4-11797 "drnes063_l_94015" FBIS-NES-94-063 Daily Report 30 Mar 1994 ISRAEL NRP Urges Soldiers To Disobey Evacuation Order NRP Urges Soldiers To Disobey Evacuation Order TA3003110794 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1000 GMT 30 Mar 94 TA3003110794 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Hebrew BFN [Excerpt] The National Religious Party [NRP] Knesset faction supports the halakic injunction of Rabbis Yisra'eli, Shapira, and Neriya, according to which IDF [Israel Defense Forces] soldiers should disobey the order to evacuate Jews from Hebron. The NRP faction states that the evacuation of Jews from Hebron is a red line from the public point of view and that following the halakic ruling it is also a halakic red line. [passage omitted]
